  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0dba\u0d9c\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc4\u0dab\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0da7\u0db1\u0dca  \u0d91.\u0da2\u0dcf.\u0db4 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "UNP party members celebrate the President's victory",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "As the 8th Executive President of the Democratic People's Government of Sri Lanka, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe was elected today (20th) in the secret ballot held in the Parliament, a group of United National Party members in Hatton town expressed their happiness by lighting firecrackers.",
        "Our camera captured how the United National Party members gathered near the clock tower in the center of Hatton and expressed their happiness by lighting firecrackers.",
        "The United National Party members who spoke to the media said that the current President Ranil Wickramasinghe is the only leader who can rebuild the motherland that has fallen economically.",
        "The United National Party said that all the MPs representing the Parliament should support the current President Ranil Wickramasinghe to abandon political opinions and rebuild the country economically."
      ],
